461
00:25:36,576 --> 00:25:37,911
DO NOT HIT IT.

462
00:25:39,621 --> 00:25:40,580
LOCKED IN, SIR.

463
00:25:40,706 --> 00:25:41,539
FIRE.

464
00:25:50,049 --> 00:25:51,842
REACTION, MR. SULU?

465
00:25:51,967 --> 00:25:53,302
NONE, SIR.

466
00:25:53,427 --> 00:25:55,054
THEY'RE STILL
APPROACHING US.

467
00:26:04,230 --> 00:26:06,606
APPARENTLY A SHOT
ACROSS THE BOW ISN'T
SUFFICIENTLY CONVINCING.

468
00:26:10,069 --> 00:26:13,447
PREPARE TO LOCK PHASERS
INTO THE HEART OF
THE COMMUNITY.

469
00:26:18,244 --> 00:26:19,119
LOCKED IN, SIR.

470
00:26:19,245 --> 00:26:20,329
FIRE.

471
00:26:21,747 --> 00:26:22,831
SCOTTY!

472
00:26:22,956 --> 00:26:24,750
OH!

473
00:26:24,875 --> 00:26:27,211
MIRA!

474
00:26:27,336 --> 00:26:28,628
MIRA.

475
00:26:28,754 --> 00:26:30,172
Sulu: THE PHASERS
SEEM TO HAVE STOPPED
THEIR APPROACH.

476
00:26:30,297 --> 00:26:32,590
THEY'RE HOLDING POSITION.

477
00:26:32,716 --> 00:26:34,510
LOCK IN FOR
ANOTHER BLAST.

478
00:26:34,634 --> 00:26:36,220
LOCKED IN, SIR.

479
00:26:36,345 --> 00:26:37,471
Scotty: CAPTAIN!

480
00:26:40,766 --> 00:26:43,936
CAPTAIN, THE PHASER SHOTS--
THEY'RE KILLING MIRA!

481
00:26:44,061 --> 00:26:45,563
KILLING
LIEUTENANT ROMAINE?

482
00:26:45,687 --> 00:26:46,772
AYE. WHEN YOU
FIRED THE PHASERS,

483
00:26:46,897 --> 00:26:48,148
THEY STUNNED HER
AND SHE CRUMPLED.

484
00:26:48,274 --> 00:26:49,900
ANOTHER SHOT
AND YOU'LL KILL HER!

485
00:26:51,944 --> 00:26:53,529
GET HER TO SICK BAY
AT ONCE.

486
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,533
READY FOR FIRING,
CAPTAIN.

487
00:27:01,495 --> 00:27:02,662
CANCEL THAT ORDER.

488
00:27:11,797 --> 00:27:13,340
ANOTHER ATTACK
ON THAT ALIEN LIFE FORM

489
00:27:13,466 --> 00:27:14,967
WILL KILL
LIEUTENANT ROMAINE.

490
00:27:15,092 --> 00:27:16,385
IT APPEARS SO.

491
00:27:16,510 --> 00:27:18,678
IF SHE IS TO SURVIVE,
WE CAN'T ATTACK.

492
00:27:18,804 --> 00:27:20,055
NOT DIRECTLY.

493
00:27:20,180 --> 00:27:21,932
CAN THE COMPUTER
SUPPLY A DEFENSE

494
00:27:22,057 --> 00:27:23,476
BASED ON ALL
THE DATA YOU'VE
BEEN ACCUMULATING?

495
00:27:23,601 --> 00:27:24,768
NEGATIVE, CAPTAIN.

496
00:27:24,893 --> 00:27:27,645
I HAVE NOT BEEN ABLE TO GATHER
SUFFICIENT DATA FOR THAT.

497
00:27:27,771 --> 00:27:31,400
CAPTAIN, THERE IS ONLY
ONE POSSIBLE DEFENSE--

498
00:27:31,525 --> 00:27:33,319
IF WE CAN FIND
AN ENVIRONMENT

499
00:27:33,444 --> 00:27:35,695
WHICH IS DEADLY
TO THE ALIEN FORM.

500
00:27:35,821 --> 00:27:38,782
AND YET ISOLATE
THE GIRL FROM
ITS DEADLY EFFECTS.

501
00:27:45,372 --> 00:27:46,706
CAPTAIN KIRK
TO DR. McCOY.

502
00:27:46,832 --> 00:27:48,000
McCoy: YES, CAPTAIN?

503
00:27:48,125 --> 00:27:50,169
IS THE GIRL
WELL ENOUGH
TO BE QUESTIONED?

504
00:27:50,294 --> 00:27:52,045
I CAN HAVE HER READY
IN A FEW MINUTES.

505
00:27:52,171 --> 00:27:54,881
HAVE THE LIEUTENANT
AND MR. SCOTT

506
00:27:55,007 --> 00:27:56,800
IN THE BRIEFING ROOM
AS QUICKLY
AS POSSIBLE.

507
00:27:56,925 --> 00:28:00,095
BRING ALL AVAILABLE
BIOGRAPHICAL MATERIAL
WITH YOU.

508
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:02,598
KIRK OUT.
MR. SPOCK, COME WITH ME.

509
00:28:13,817 --> 00:28:15,944
GO EASY ON HER, JIM.
SHE'S IN A PRETTY BAD STATE.

510
00:28:16,069 --> 00:28:17,821
I'LL TRY.

511
00:28:20,698 --> 00:28:21,575
LIEUTENANT ROMAINE.

512
00:28:31,751 --> 00:28:34,380
I DIDN'T MEAN TO BE
UNCOOPERATIVE, DOCTOR.

513
00:28:34,505 --> 00:28:36,298
OF COURSE YOU DIDN'T.
I TOLD THE CAPTAIN.

514
00:28:36,423 --> 00:28:38,592
WE MUST
GET TO UNDERSTAND
WHAT IS HAPPENING.

515
00:28:38,717 --> 00:28:40,969
I'LL TELL YOU
EVERYTHING I KNOW.

516
00:28:41,094 --> 00:28:44,890
SHIP'S INVESTIGATIVE
PROCEDURES ARE
SOMETIMES CONFUSING

517
00:28:45,015 --> 00:28:45,807
TO A NEW CREWMAN.

518
00:28:45,932 --> 00:28:47,726
DON'T LET US
UPSET YOU.

519
00:28:47,851 --> 00:28:49,395
I TRUST ALL OF YOU
IMPLICITLY.

520
00:28:52,981 --> 00:28:54,107
I WANT TO HELP.

521
00:28:54,233 --> 00:28:55,568
Kirk: THIS
INVESTIGATION

522
00:28:55,693 --> 00:28:57,653
HAS BEEN PROMPTED
BY 2 EVENTS.

523
00:28:57,777 --> 00:29:00,113
FIRST IS THE TIME
YOU PASSED OUT
ON THE BRIDGE,

524
00:29:00,239 --> 00:29:02,241
AND THE SECOND
IS WHEN WE FIRED

525
00:29:02,366 --> 00:29:04,284
OUR MAIN PHASERS
INTO THAT FORCE
THAT IS ATTACKING US

526
00:29:04,410 --> 00:29:06,412
AND SERIOUSLY
INJURED YOU.

527
00:29:06,537 --> 00:29:08,955
YOU MUSTN'T WORRY
ABOUT HURTING ME.

528
00:29:09,081 --> 00:29:11,667
NOW, THIS IS
HOW WE'LL PROCEED.

529
00:29:11,791 --> 00:29:15,837
MR. SPOCK HAS ALL
THE INFORMATION
AVAILABLE TO US

530
00:29:15,962 --> 00:29:17,964
ABOUT OUR ATTACKERS.

531
00:29:18,090 --> 00:29:19,841
DR. McCOY HAS ACCESS

532
00:29:19,966 --> 00:29:22,595
TO STARFLEET'S
EXHAUSTIVE FILES ON YOU.

533
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:23,596
A COMPARISON
OF THE TWO

534
00:29:23,721 --> 00:29:25,598
MAY TURN UP
SOME IMPROBABLE CONNECTION

535
00:29:25,723 --> 00:29:29,184
WHICH MAY PROTECT YOU
AND OURSELVES.

536
00:29:29,309 --> 00:29:31,395
ALL RIGHT, GENTLEMEN?

537
00:29:31,520 --> 00:29:33,313
DR. MCCOY,
WILL YOU PROCEED?

538
00:29:39,403 --> 00:29:41,071
ROMAINE, MIRA.
LIEUTENANT.

539
00:29:41,196 --> 00:29:43,699
PLACE OF BIRTH,
MARTIAN COLONY NUMBER 3.

540
00:29:43,823 --> 00:29:45,992
PARENTS, LYDIA ROMAINE,
DECEASED.

541
00:29:46,118 --> 00:29:47,703
JACQUES ROMAINE,
CHIEF ENGINEER,

542
00:29:47,827 --> 00:29:50,789
STARFLEET, RETIRED.

543
00:29:50,914 --> 00:29:52,541
MR. SPOCK, ARE YOU PREPARED
WITH THE BACKGROUND HISTORY

544
00:29:52,666 --> 00:29:53,792
OF THE ATTACKERS?

545
00:29:53,917 --> 00:29:54,460
I AM, CAPTAIN.

546
00:29:54,585 --> 00:29:56,503
I HAVE FED
ALL OBTAINABLE DATA

547
00:29:56,629 --> 00:29:57,546
TO THE MAIN COMPUTER.

548
00:29:57,671 --> 00:29:58,880
IT SHOULD BE
READY TO SUPPLY

549
00:29:59,005 --> 00:29:59,965
WHATEVER CONCLUSIONS
ARE POSSIBLE.

550
00:30:00,090 --> 00:30:02,468
THANK YOU.

551
00:30:02,593 --> 00:30:03,761
MR. SULU,
WHAT IS THE STATUS

552
00:30:03,885 --> 00:30:05,095
OF OUR FRIENDS
UP THERE?

553
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:06,388
STATUS UNCHANGED.

554
00:30:06,513 --> 00:30:08,474
THEY ARE STILL WITH US
AND KEEPING THE SAME DISTANCE.

555
00:30:08,599 --> 00:30:10,225
CONTINUE EVASIVE
MANEUVERS.

556
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:10,892
KEEP ME INFORMED.

557
00:30:11,017 --> 00:30:13,186
KIRK OUT.

558
00:30:13,312 --> 00:30:15,314
DOCTOR, YOU HAVE
A MEDICAL RECORD

559
00:30:15,439 --> 00:30:17,232
OF LIEUTENANT ROMAINE
AVAILABLE?

560
00:30:17,357 --> 00:30:18,525
YES, CAPTAIN.

561
00:30:18,651 --> 00:30:20,736
I'D LIKE A FEW ITEMS
FROM HER PSYCHOLOGICAL

562
00:30:20,860 --> 00:30:21,612
PROFILE CHECKED.

563
00:30:26,199 --> 00:30:28,494
ANY HISTORY OF
PSYCHOSOMATIC ILLNESS?

564
00:30:31,455 --> 00:30:34,416
OCCASIONAL AND TEENAGE
ROUTINE INCIDENTS.

565
00:30:34,541 --> 00:30:36,794
ANY EVIDENCE
OF INVOLUNTARY
OR UNCONSCIOUS

566
00:30:36,918 --> 00:30:38,211
TELEPATHIC ABILITIES?

567
00:30:42,090 --> 00:30:43,133
NONE.

568
00:30:43,258 --> 00:30:46,595
ANY PATHOLOGICAL
OR UNUSUAL

569
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:48,221
EMPATHIC RESPONSES?

570
00:30:50,932 --> 00:30:52,934
NO, CAPTAIN,
NOT EMPATHIC.

571
00:30:53,059 --> 00:30:55,729
HOWEVER, AN EXTREMELY
FLEXIBLE

572
00:30:55,854 --> 00:30:58,398
AND PLIANT RESPONSE TO NEW
LEARNING SITUATIONS

573
00:30:58,524 --> 00:30:59,608
IS HIGHLY MARKED.

574
00:31:00,984 --> 00:31:02,027
GO AHEAD, DOCTOR.

575
00:31:02,152 --> 00:31:03,654
RIGHT AFTER OUR PHASERS
HIT THAT THING,

576
00:31:03,779 --> 00:31:06,824
I GAVE LIEUTENANT ROMAINE
A STANDARD STEINMAN ANALYSIS,

577
00:31:06,948 --> 00:31:08,200
AND THE RESULTS
MIGHT BE INTERESTING.

578
00:31:08,325 --> 00:31:09,409
UH-HUH. GO AHEAD.

579
00:31:12,621 --> 00:31:15,708
A COMPARISON OF OUR STEINMAN
WITH STARFLEET RECORDS

580
00:31:15,833 --> 00:31:20,170
SHOWS THAT LIEUTENANT ROMAINE'S
FINGERPRINTS, VOICE ANALYSIS,

581
00:31:20,295 --> 00:31:24,257
ALL EXTERNAL FACTORS REMAIN
EXACTLY THE SAME AS BEFORE.

582
00:31:24,383 --> 00:31:27,636
HOWEVER, ACCORDING TO
2 HYPERENCEPHALOGRAMS,

583
00:31:27,761 --> 00:31:29,888
HER BRAIN WAVE PATTERN
HAS BEEN ALTERED.

584
00:31:33,559 --> 00:31:34,852
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE!

585
00:31:34,976 --> 00:31:36,812
THAT'S WHAT
I WAS TAUGHT.

586
00:31:36,936 --> 00:31:39,648
BUT THE BCP IS JUST AS
CONSISTENT AS FINGERPRINTS.

587
00:31:39,773 --> 00:31:40,607
LET'S SEE IT.

588
00:31:48,448 --> 00:31:50,950
DR. McCOY, ACCORDING
TO YOUR RECORDS,

589
00:31:51,076 --> 00:31:54,830
LIEUTENANT ROMAINE
HAS SHOWED NO ABNORMAL
TELEPATHIC POWERS.

590
00:31:54,954 --> 00:31:56,498
McCoy:
THAT'S RIGHT, SPOCK,

591
00:31:56,623 --> 00:31:59,877
BUT EXCEPTIONAL PLIANCY
WAS INDICATED.

592
00:32:00,001 --> 00:32:02,003
THAT MIGHT BE A FACTOR.

593
00:32:02,128 --> 00:32:03,505
Spock:
AND YOU ARE SURE

594
00:32:03,630 --> 00:32:05,632
THAT THIS IS
THE CORRECT SLIDE?

595
00:32:05,758 --> 00:32:09,511
YES, MR. SPOCK.
THAT IS TAPE DECK "D"--

596
00:32:09,636 --> 00:32:12,389
BRAIN CIRCUITRY PATTERN
OF LIEUTENANT MIRA ROMAINE.

597
00:32:12,514 --> 00:32:15,350
GENTLEMEN,
IT ALSO
HAPPENS TO BE

598
00:32:15,475 --> 00:32:18,144
TAPE "H"--
THE IMPULSE
TRACKING

599
00:32:18,270 --> 00:32:21,231
OBTAINED
FROM THE ALIEN
LIFE UNITS.

600
00:32:21,356 --> 00:32:23,400
McCoy: NURSE CHAPEL
FOLLOWED THIS EVERY
STEP OF THE WAY.

601
00:32:23,525 --> 00:32:24,860
THERE CAN BE NO ERROR.

602
00:32:24,984 --> 00:32:26,069
CHECK IT, SPOCK.

603
00:32:34,453 --> 00:32:36,663
AS I SAID, CAPTAIN,
THIS IS THE TRACKING

604
00:32:36,789 --> 00:32:38,791
OBTAINED DURING
THE LAST SHIELDED RUN.

605
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:45,297
COMPUTER,
RUN A DETAILED
COMPARISON--

606
00:32:45,422 --> 00:32:47,048
BRAIN CIRCUITRY
PATTERNS,

607
00:32:47,173 --> 00:32:50,051
TAPE "D"
AND TAPE "H."

608
00:32:50,176 --> 00:32:51,136
Computer voice:
COMPARISON--

609
00:32:51,261 --> 00:32:54,973
TAPE "D," BRAIN CIRCUITRY
PATTERNS OF LIEUTENANT
MIRA ROMAINE

610
00:32:55,098 --> 00:32:58,769
AND TAPE "H," BRAIN CIRCUITRY
PATTERNS OF ALIEN LIFE UNIT

611
00:32:58,894 --> 00:33:00,312
IDENTICAL.

612
00:33:00,437 --> 00:33:01,688
IDENTICAL.

613
00:33:04,858 --> 00:33:06,151
FASCINATING.

614
00:33:09,237 --> 00:33:10,405
THERE HAS BEEN NO ERROR.

615
00:33:10,530 --> 00:33:13,241
DR. McCOY
IS CORRECT, CAPTAIN.

616
00:33:13,366 --> 00:33:15,452
THERE IS AN IDENTITY
OF MINDS TAKING PLACE

617
00:33:15,577 --> 00:33:19,623
BETWEEN THE ALIEN
BEINGS AND THE MIND
OF LIEUTENANT ROMAINE.

618
00:33:19,748 --> 00:33:21,917
THEIR THOUGHTS...

619
00:33:22,041 --> 00:33:23,627
ARE BECOMING HERS.

620
00:33:31,134 --> 00:33:32,594
BRIDGE TO CAPTAIN KIRK.

621
00:33:32,719 --> 00:33:35,013
THE ALIEN IS
NO LONGER MAINTAINING
ITS DISTANCE.

622
00:33:35,138 --> 00:33:37,349
CONTINUE EVASIVE ACTION.
KEEP ME INFORMED.
KIRK OUT.

623
00:33:46,692 --> 00:33:48,401
MIRA HAS TRIED TO TELL ME
ALL ALONG

624
00:33:48,527 --> 00:33:51,488
THAT SHE WAS SEEING THINGS
IN ADVANCE.

625
00:33:51,613 --> 00:33:53,657
WHY DIDN'T YOU
REPORT IT?

626
00:33:53,782 --> 00:33:54,867
YOU DON'T REPORT
SPACE SICKNESS.

627
00:33:54,992 --> 00:33:57,703
THAT'S ALL
I THOUGHT IT WAS.

628
00:33:57,828 --> 00:33:59,037
WHAT DID SHE SEE?

629
00:33:59,162 --> 00:34:02,165
FIRST THE ATTACK
ON THE SHIP,

630
00:34:02,290 --> 00:34:05,418
THE ATTACK
ON MEMORY ALPHA,

631
00:34:05,544 --> 00:34:08,881
AND...THE TIME
WE NEARLY LOST HER.

632
00:34:10,966 --> 00:34:12,843
THOSE WERE ALL
ACTS CARRIED OUT
BY OUR ATTACKER.

633
00:34:12,968 --> 00:34:14,636
AND...

634
00:34:21,018 --> 00:34:22,060
AND...

635
00:34:24,021 --> 00:34:25,063
YES, SCOTTY?

636
00:34:27,941 --> 00:34:29,026
WHAT ELSE?

637
00:34:30,903 --> 00:34:32,863
I THOUGHT FOR A MOMENT

638
00:34:32,988 --> 00:34:33,906
THERE WAS SOMETHING ELSE,

639
00:34:34,031 --> 00:34:37,200
BUT...I GUESS
I WAS WRONG.

640
00:34:37,325 --> 00:34:38,994
WAS HE WRONG,
LIEUTENANT?

641
00:34:39,118 --> 00:34:41,413
YES, THERE WAS
ONE OTHER TIME.

642
00:34:41,538 --> 00:34:42,956
WHAT DID YOU SEE?

643
00:34:43,081 --> 00:34:44,666
I SAW SCOTTY.

644
00:34:44,791 --> 00:34:47,002
WHERE?

645
00:34:47,126 --> 00:34:48,879
I DON'T KNOW.

646
00:34:49,004 --> 00:34:50,088
WHAT WAS HE DOING?

647
00:34:58,263 --> 00:34:59,639
HE WAS DYING.

648
00:35:04,728 --> 00:35:06,939
NOW I UNDERSTAND
WHAT'S BEEN
HAPPENING.

649
00:35:09,357 --> 00:35:12,027
I'VE BEEN SEEING
THROUGH...

650
00:35:12,151 --> 00:35:14,404
THROUGH ANOTHER MIND.

651
00:35:14,529 --> 00:35:17,699
I'VE BEEN FLOODED
WITH THOUGHTS...

652
00:35:17,824 --> 00:35:19,576
NOT MY OWN.

653
00:35:19,701 --> 00:35:21,536
THEY CONTROL ME!
OH, SCOTTY.

654
00:35:21,661 --> 00:35:23,622
SCOTTY,
I'D RATHER DIE
THAN HURT YOU!

655
00:35:23,747 --> 00:35:25,040
I'D RATHER DIE.

656
00:35:25,164 --> 00:35:27,709
ALL RIGHT, NOW.

657
00:35:27,834 --> 00:35:32,505
WHAT'S ALL THIS TALK
OF DYING?

658
00:35:32,631 --> 00:35:36,885
THEY'VE CALLED THE TURN ON US
3 OUT OF 4 TIMES.

659
00:35:37,010 --> 00:35:40,806
NOW, THAT'S A BETTER AVERAGE
THAN ANYBODY DESERVES.

660
00:35:40,931 --> 00:35:42,933
IT'S OUR TURN NOW.

661
00:35:43,058 --> 00:35:44,684
WE'LL FIGHT THEM.

662
00:35:44,810 --> 00:35:49,064
SO LET'S NOT HEAR
ANYTHING MORE ABOUT DYING.

663
00:35:49,188 --> 00:35:51,190
[SIGNAL FROM BRIDGE]

664
00:35:51,316 --> 00:35:52,191
KIRK HERE.

665
00:35:52,317 --> 00:35:53,234
SULU, CAPTAIN.

666
00:35:53,359 --> 00:35:55,320
ALL EVASION TACTICS
CARRIED OUT AS ORDERED.

667
00:35:55,445 --> 00:35:56,863
Kirk: WHAT SUCCESS
DID YOU HAVE?

668
00:35:56,989 --> 00:35:59,449
IT'S BEEN USELESS,
CAPTAIN.

669
00:35:59,574 --> 00:36:00,784
Spock: AT THEIR
PRESENT FORCE,

670
00:36:00,909 --> 00:36:03,036
THEY WILL GET
THROUGH THE SHIELDS
THIS TIME, CAPTAIN.

671
00:36:05,246 --> 00:36:06,915
WARP 8, MR. SULU.

672
00:36:07,040 --> 00:36:08,917
YES, SIR.

673
00:36:09,042 --> 00:36:10,418
THEY'LL BE HERE
VERY SOON.

674
00:36:12,295 --> 00:36:15,757
THEY MAY DESTROY YOU
AND US AS THEY DID
MEMORY ALPHA.

675
00:36:15,882 --> 00:36:18,969
YOU ARE
ESPECIALLY SUSCEPTIBLE
TO THEIR WILL.

676
00:36:19,094 --> 00:36:23,140
BUT WE HAVE...
ONE CHANCE TO SURVIVE.

677
00:36:23,264 --> 00:36:24,975
DON'T RESIST.

678
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:28,436
LET THEM BEGIN
TO FUNCTION THROUGH YOU.

679
00:36:30,188 --> 00:36:33,942
IF WE CAN CONTROL
THAT MOMENT,

680
00:36:34,067 --> 00:36:35,610
WE HAVE A CHANCE.
WILL YOU TRY?

681
00:36:40,239 --> 00:36:41,992
TELL ME
WHAT TO DO.

682
00:36:44,369 --> 00:36:45,871
CAPTAIN KIRK
TO MEDICAL LAB.

683
00:36:45,996 --> 00:36:47,455
MEDICAL LAB HERE, SIR.

