00:37:18,403 --> 00:37:21,280
GENERAL QUARTERS--
SECURITY CONDITION 3.

694
00:37:21,406 --> 00:37:22,782
INTRUDER ALERT.

695
00:37:22,908 --> 00:37:27,079
REPEAT. GENERAL QUARTERS--
SECURITY CONDITION 3.

696
00:37:27,204 --> 00:37:28,413
INTRUDER ALERT.

697
00:37:38,965 --> 00:37:41,300
Kirk: AS SOON
AS SHE HAS ENTERED
THE GRAVITY CHAMBER,

698
00:37:41,426 --> 00:37:42,677
SECURE ALL PORTS.

699
00:37:50,977 --> 00:37:53,021
DON'T TOUCH ME, SCOTTY!

700
00:37:53,146 --> 00:37:54,189
STAY AWAY.

701
00:38:01,738 --> 00:38:03,573
[LOW-PITCHED CROAKING]

702
00:38:13,332 --> 00:38:15,585
WE'VE LOST HER
TO THEM.

703
00:38:19,464 --> 00:38:20,298
STAY WHERE YOU ARE.

704
00:38:20,423 --> 00:38:22,134
SHE COULD KILL US ALL
IN THIS STATE.

705
00:38:22,259 --> 00:38:24,469
SHE WILL, UNLESS WE
ARE ABLE TO COMPLETE

706
00:38:24,594 --> 00:38:26,096
WHAT THE CAPTAIN
HAS PLANNED.

707
00:38:26,221 --> 00:38:28,098
STAY WITH US,
MIRA.

708
00:38:28,223 --> 00:38:29,975
PLEASE STAY!

709
00:38:30,100 --> 00:38:32,144
I'M TRYING.

710
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:38,399
I WANT TO BE WITH YOU.

711
00:38:38,524 --> 00:38:40,693
THEY ARE TOO STRONG.

712
00:38:40,819 --> 00:38:42,320
DON'T LOSE YOURSELF
TO THEM.

713
00:38:42,445 --> 00:38:43,989
HOLD ON!

714
00:38:55,167 --> 00:38:59,296
I AM MIRA ROMAINE.

715
00:38:59,420 --> 00:39:04,425
I WILL BE
WHO I CHOOSE TO BE.

716
00:39:06,011 --> 00:39:08,054
Mira: I WI--

717
00:39:08,180 --> 00:39:09,597
STAY AWAY, SCOTTY!

718
00:39:12,558 --> 00:39:13,768
THEY'RE WITH ME.

719
00:39:15,478 --> 00:39:18,481
THEY WILL KILL YOU.

720
00:39:18,606 --> 00:39:19,649
YOU WON'T
LET THEM.

721
00:39:31,577 --> 00:39:34,580
Deep voice:
SHE CANNOT STOP US.

722
00:39:34,706 --> 00:39:36,582
YOU CANNOT PREVENT IT.

723
00:39:38,918 --> 00:39:39,836
Scotty: MIRA...

724
00:39:39,961 --> 00:39:42,714
MIRA!

725
00:39:42,839 --> 00:39:44,507
CAPTAIN.

726
00:39:44,632 --> 00:39:45,591
THAT'S NOT
MIRA TALKING.

727
00:39:45,717 --> 00:39:48,094
CAPTAIN, WE MUST
DEAL WITH THEM
DIRECTLY,

728
00:39:48,220 --> 00:39:50,889
NOW, WHILE SHE
STILL RETAINS
PARTIAL IDENTITY.

729
00:39:51,014 --> 00:39:52,431
WE CAN SPEAK
TO THEM.

730
00:39:52,557 --> 00:39:54,642
THEY WILL ANSWER
USING HER VOICE.

731
00:40:04,361 --> 00:40:06,612
I'M CAPTAIN
JAMES KIRK

732
00:40:06,738 --> 00:40:08,489
OF THE SPACESHIP
"ENTERPRISE."

733
00:40:11,368 --> 00:40:13,661
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

734
00:40:13,786 --> 00:40:16,748
Deep voice:
YES, WE UNDERSTAND YOU.

735
00:40:16,873 --> 00:40:19,625
WE HAVE SEARCHED
FOR A MILLENNIUM

736
00:40:19,751 --> 00:40:23,004
FOR ONE THROUGH WHOM
WE CAN SEE AND SPEAK

737
00:40:23,129 --> 00:40:26,758
AND HEAR AND LIVE OUT
OUR LIVES.

738
00:40:26,883 --> 00:40:28,093
WHO ARE YOU?

739
00:40:28,218 --> 00:40:31,304
WE ARE FROM ZETAR.

740
00:40:31,429 --> 00:40:33,639
THAT IS ONE OF THE PLANETS
WHERE ALL HUMANOID LIFE
WAS DESTROYED.

741
00:40:35,474 --> 00:40:38,061
YOU CAN'T BE
FROM ZETAR.

742
00:40:38,186 --> 00:40:41,480
ALL LIFE WAS
DESTROYED THERE
LONG AGO.

743
00:40:41,606 --> 00:40:45,277
YES. ALL CORPOREAL LIFE
WAS DESTROYED.

744
00:40:45,402 --> 00:40:46,611
THEN WHAT ARE YOU?

745
00:40:46,736 --> 00:40:49,447
THE DESIRES,
THE HOPES, THE MIND,

746
00:40:49,572 --> 00:40:53,492
AND THE WILL OF
THE LAST 100 OF ZETAR.

747
00:40:53,618 --> 00:40:56,913
THE FORCE OF OUR LIFE
COULD NOT BE WIPED OUT.

748
00:40:57,038 --> 00:40:58,831
ALL THINGS DIE.

749
00:40:58,957 --> 00:41:01,167
AT THE PROPER TIME.

750
00:41:01,293 --> 00:41:03,836
OUR PLANET WAS DYING.

751
00:41:03,962 --> 00:41:06,672
WE WERE DETERMINED
TO LIVE ON.

752
00:41:06,798 --> 00:41:09,008
AT THE PEAK
OF OUR PLANS TO GO,

753
00:41:09,134 --> 00:41:12,470
A SUDDEN FINAL DISASTER
STRUCK US DOWN,

754
00:41:12,595 --> 00:41:17,183
BUT THE FORCE OF
OUR LIVES SURVIVED.

755
00:41:17,309 --> 00:41:22,439
AT LAST WE HAVE FOUND
SOMEONE THROUGH WHOM
WE CAN LIVE IT OUT.

756
00:41:22,563 --> 00:41:25,233
THE BODY OF THE ONE
YOU INHABIT

757
00:41:25,358 --> 00:41:27,277
HAS ITS OWN LIFE TO LEAD.

758
00:41:27,402 --> 00:41:29,862
SHE WILL ACCEPT OURS.

759
00:41:29,988 --> 00:41:31,739
SHE WILL NOT.

760
00:41:31,864 --> 00:41:34,075
SHE IS FIGHTING
FOR HER OWN IDENTITY.

761
00:41:34,200 --> 00:41:37,495
HER MIND WILL ACCEPT
OUR THOUGHTS.

762
00:41:37,620 --> 00:41:41,582
OUR LIVES
WILL BE FULFILLED.

763
00:41:41,707 --> 00:41:44,669
WILL SHE LEARN
THE WAY THE PEOPLE
ON MEMORY ALPHA LEARNED?

764
00:41:44,794 --> 00:41:46,629
WE DID NOT WISH TO KILL.

765
00:41:46,754 --> 00:41:48,173
BUT YOU DID KILL.

766
00:41:48,298 --> 00:41:53,178
NO. RESISTING US
KILLED THOSE PEOPLE.

767
00:41:53,303 --> 00:41:55,430
WE DID NOT KILL THEM.

768
00:41:55,554 --> 00:41:58,641
THE PRICE OF YOUR
SURVIVAL IS TOO HIGH.

769
00:41:58,766 --> 00:42:00,852
WE ONLY WANT THE GIRL.

770
00:42:00,977 --> 00:42:02,020
YOU CAN'T HAVE HER.

771
00:42:02,145 --> 00:42:05,857
YOU'RE ENTITLED
TO YOUR OWN LIFE,
BUT NOT ANOTHER'S.

772
00:42:12,571 --> 00:42:15,658
Mira's voice:
LIFE WAS GIVEN TO ME.

773
00:42:18,411 --> 00:42:20,163
IT IS MINE.

774
00:42:20,288 --> 00:42:23,791
I WANT TO LIVE IT OUT.

775
00:42:23,916 --> 00:42:25,960
I WILL--

776
00:42:27,504 --> 00:42:29,088
McCoy: THE GIRL'S
LIFE READING

777
00:42:29,214 --> 00:42:31,716
IS BECOMING A MATCH
TO THE ZETARIANS.

778
00:42:31,841 --> 00:42:34,552
SHE'S LOSING.

779
00:42:34,677 --> 00:42:37,180
Deep voice: DO NOT FIGHT US.

780
00:42:37,305 --> 00:42:39,349
THEY WILL NOT ACCEPT
THEIR OWN DEATHS.

781
00:42:43,269 --> 00:42:45,480
THEY WILL BE FORCED
TO ACCEPT IT.

782
00:42:45,604 --> 00:42:48,774
YOU WILL ALL DIE.

783
00:42:48,900 --> 00:42:51,403
CAPTAIN, IF WE CANNOT
COMPLETE THE PLAN,

784
00:42:51,528 --> 00:42:53,071
THEY WILL CARRY OUT
THEIR THREAT.

785
00:42:53,196 --> 00:42:55,448
WE MUST GET HER
INTO THE PRESSURE
CHAMBER.

786
00:42:55,573 --> 00:42:59,202
JIM, YOU REALIZE
THE PRESSURE NEEDED
TO KILL THE ZETARS

787
00:42:59,327 --> 00:43:00,995
MIGHT KILL
THE GIRL, TOO.

788
00:43:05,166 --> 00:43:06,543
MIRA WILL NOT
KILL ME.

789
00:43:31,692 --> 00:43:33,278
[ZAP]
AAH!

790
00:43:42,245 --> 00:43:45,540
I TOLD YOU
SHE WOULDN'T KILL ME.

791
00:43:45,664 --> 00:43:46,999
SECURE THE CHAMBER.

792
00:43:52,713 --> 00:43:54,132
NEUTRALIZE GRAVITY.

793
00:44:04,016 --> 00:44:05,935
THE ZETARS ARE
GROWING STRONGER.

794
00:44:06,060 --> 00:44:10,148
THE WEIGHTLESS STATE
HAS BECOME THEIR
NATURAL CONDITION.

795
00:44:10,273 --> 00:44:11,441
PRESSURIZE THE UNIT.

796
00:44:17,405 --> 00:44:19,073
BRING PRESSURE
TO 2 ATMOSPHERES

797
00:44:19,198 --> 00:44:21,075
AND THEN INCREASE
ONE ATMOSPHERE
PER SECOND.

798
00:44:40,637 --> 00:44:42,054
CONTINUE INCREASING
PRESSURE.

799
00:45:01,449 --> 00:45:03,409
PRESSURE, SPOCK,
PRESSURE.

800
00:45:08,414 --> 00:45:10,458
PRESSURE IS DANGEROUSLY
HIGH, CAPTAIN.

801
00:45:12,001 --> 00:45:13,586
IT MAY DAMAGE HER!

802
00:45:16,005 --> 00:45:17,173
CONTINUE, SPOCK.

803
00:46:03,177 --> 00:46:04,345
PRESSURE.

804
00:46:15,398 --> 00:46:16,982
McCoy:
WE'VE DONE IT, JIM.

805
00:46:17,108 --> 00:46:18,234
THEY'RE GONE.

806
00:46:24,198 --> 00:46:25,700
IT'S ALL RIGHT, MIRA.

807
00:46:25,824 --> 00:46:26,659
THEY'RE GONE.

808
00:46:29,203 --> 00:46:30,663
THEY'RE GONE!

809
00:46:40,047 --> 00:46:43,551
REDUCE THE PRESSURE
VERY, VERY GRADUALLY, SPOCK.

810
00:46:43,676 --> 00:46:46,512
WE MAY TAX MR. SCOTT'S
PATIENCE, DOCTOR.

811
00:47:00,859 --> 00:47:04,155
NOW LIE PERFECTLY
STILL, LIEUTENANT.
TRY NOT TO MOVE AT ALL.

812
00:47:04,280 --> 00:47:07,032
TAKE DEEP,
REGULAR BREATHS.

813
00:47:07,158 --> 00:47:09,661
NOW, DON'T HOLD IT.

814
00:47:09,786 --> 00:47:11,788
CONTINUE TO BREATHE DEEPLY.

815
00:47:11,912 --> 00:47:17,543
IN, OUT.
IN, OUT.

816
00:47:17,669 --> 00:47:18,961
THAT'S IT.

817
00:47:19,086 --> 00:47:20,797
NOW, YOU'LL BE IN THERE
ANOTHER 20 MINUTES,

818
00:47:20,921 --> 00:47:22,799
SO WHY DON'T YOU
JUST TRY TO RELAX?

819
00:47:27,679 --> 00:47:29,972
NOW WE HAVE ALL
THE TIME IN THE WORLD.

820
00:47:53,412 --> 00:47:54,622
BONES, ARE YOU
ABLE TO JUDGE

821
00:47:54,747 --> 00:47:56,708
THE LONG-RANGE EFFECTS
ON LIEUTENANT ROMAINE?

822
00:47:56,833 --> 00:47:59,210
WHEN THE PERSONALITY
OF A HUMAN IS INVOLVED,

823
00:47:59,335 --> 00:48:01,920
EXACT PREDICTIONS
ARE HAZARDOUS.

824
00:48:02,046 --> 00:48:04,298
PARTICULARLY WHERE HUMANS
ARE INVOLVED, DOCTOR.

825
00:48:04,423 --> 00:48:07,760
HOWEVER, DESPITE STARFLEET
JUDGMENT OF THE PLIANCY
OF THE LIEUTENANT,

826
00:48:07,884 --> 00:48:09,512
SHE PUT UP
A VALIANT STRUGGLE

827
00:48:09,637 --> 00:48:10,680
TO RETAIN HER IDENTITY,

828
00:48:10,805 --> 00:48:12,515
AND I FIND THAT
ENCOURAGING.

829
00:48:12,640 --> 00:48:14,600
DR. McCOY
IS CORRECT, CAPTAIN.

830
00:48:14,726 --> 00:48:16,644
WHILE THE TRUTH
WAS DIFFICULT TO ACCEPT,

831
00:48:16,769 --> 00:48:19,522
WHEN IT WAS REVEALED,
THE GIRL REACTED WELL.

832
00:48:19,647 --> 00:48:21,774
I WOULD SAY HER STRUGGLE
IN THIS EXPERIENCE

833
00:48:21,940 --> 00:48:24,276
WOULD STRENGTHEN
HER ENTIRE EGO STRUCTURE.

834
00:48:24,402 --> 00:48:25,695
WOULD EITHER
OF YOU CREDIT

835
00:48:25,820 --> 00:48:28,865
SCOTTY'S STEADFAST BELIEF
IN HER AS A FACTOR?

836
00:48:28,989 --> 00:48:32,284
YOU MEAN
LOVE AS MOTIVATION?

837
00:48:34,161 --> 00:48:37,248
HMM. HUMANS DO CLAIM
A GREAT DEAL

838
00:48:37,373 --> 00:48:40,167
FOR THAT
PARTICULAR EMOTION.

839
00:48:40,292 --> 00:48:42,919
I SUPPOSE IT IS
POSSIBLE. HOWEVER--

840
00:48:43,045 --> 00:48:44,672
THERE ARE NO HOWEVERS
ABOUT IT, MR. SPOCK.

841
00:48:44,797 --> 00:48:46,048
IT WAS A FACTOR,

842
00:48:46,173 --> 00:48:49,343
AND IT WILL BE
A FACTOR IN
THE GIRL'S RECOVERY.

843
00:48:49,468 --> 00:48:50,344
Kirk: DO I TAKE IT
BOTH OF YOU

844
00:48:50,469 --> 00:48:52,889
AGREE THAT
LIEUTENANT ROMAINE

845
00:48:53,013 --> 00:48:55,433
NEED NOT RETURN
TO STARBASE FOR
FURTHER TREATMENT?

846
00:48:55,558 --> 00:48:57,810
WELL, I SHOULD THINK WORK
WOULD BE A BETTER THERAPY.

847
00:48:57,934 --> 00:48:59,520
LOGICAL.

848
00:49:02,356 --> 00:49:04,358
CAPTAIN KIRK
TO MR. SCOTT.

849
00:49:04,483 --> 00:49:05,484
SCOTT HERE, SIR.

850
00:49:05,610 --> 00:49:07,361
MR. SCOTT, HOW IS
LIEUTENANT ROMAINE?

851
00:49:07,486 --> 00:49:07,986
BEAUTIFUL, CAPTAIN.

852
00:49:08,112 --> 00:49:09,530
YES, MR. SCOTT.

853
00:49:09,655 --> 00:49:11,407
DO I TAKE IT
YOU SAY THAT

854
00:49:11,532 --> 00:49:12,991
SHE IS
FIT FOR DUTY?

855
00:49:13,117 --> 00:49:14,368
POSITIVELY, CAPTAIN.

856
00:49:14,493 --> 00:49:15,994
THANK YOU.

857
00:49:16,120 --> 00:49:17,413
KIRK TO BRIDGE.

858
00:49:17,538 --> 00:49:18,623
SULU, CAPTAIN.

859
00:49:18,748 --> 00:49:20,875
MR. SULU, SET COURSE
FOR MEMORY ALPHA.

860
00:49:20,999 --> 00:49:22,501
LIEUTENANT ROMAINE
HAS A LOT OF WORK
TO DO THERE.

861
00:49:22,627 --> 00:49:23,878
YES, SIR.

862
00:49:24,002 --> 00:49:27,882
WELL, THIS IS
AN "ENTERPRISE"
FIRST.

863
00:49:29,801 --> 00:49:33,095
DR. McCOY, MR. SPOCK,
AND ENGINEER SCOTT

864
00:49:33,220 --> 00:49:36,515
FIND THEMSELVES
IN COMPLETE AGREEMENT.

865
00:49:36,641 --> 00:49:38,517
CAN I STAND THE STRAIN?

866
00:49:42,313 --> 00:49:43,397
[CHUCKLES]
